{"tid":925884,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[選擇困難症]買唔買Kindle好(3)暨交流區","createTime":"2018-12-03T04:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T17:19:27.000Z","uid":142247,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c2d9fcf49cdd67b37eca56a6bdbc4f18dbf47967","tid":925884,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:59:31.000Z","msg":"估唔到會開到三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有問題嘅巴絲可以花小小時間睇咗呢頁先<br />\n（辛苦咁多位巴絲幫手整理）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果都係解決唔到你嘅問題嘅話歡迎發問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地會好樂意解答你嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n常見問題整理<br />\n<br />\nCalibre(入書落Kindle嘅好幫手）<br />\n下載link：<a href=\"https://calibre-ebook.com/download\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcalibre-ebook.com%2Fdownload&d=JdofEqXGygwe9bBNhTug2ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=80b344f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://calibre-ebook.com/download</a><br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">用ipad睇書唔得咩，點解要買多部eink Reader?<br />\neink reader好似睇</span><br />\n真書一樣唔會每隻眼咁容易攰同唔舒服<br />\n長期睇書就啱晒你<br />\n但如果睇開pdf既就用返ipad之類既tablet<br />\n因為機能所限<br />\n一zoom in out會lag到想扔爛部機<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">咁多E ink Reader，買邊部好？</span><br />\n睇英文書就買kindle啦<br />\n中文書都有但好少正體（亦都可以係其他地方買完再入落Kindle)<br />\n唔想咁麻煩咁睇正體書就可以揀返 readmoo kobo 之類ereader <br />\n<br />\n而Kindle都分不同版本<br />\n根據價錢就低至高同埋硬件分別係<br />\nKindle (冇燈冇實體掣）<br />\nKindle paperwhite (有燈冇實體掣)<br />\nKindle oasis (有燈有實體掣）<br />\n而有好多features同大小都有分別嘅<br />\n可以Google睇下<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">邊度有繁體電子書賣？</span><br />\nreadmoo<br />\nkobo<br />\nGoogle play<br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">點樣簡體轉繁體？</span><br />\ncalibre（<a href=\"https://www.mobileread.com/forums/showthread.php?t=275572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobileread.com%2Fforums%2Fshowthread.php%3Ft%3D275572&d=JdofEqXGygwe9bBNhTug2ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=58dda5e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mobileread.com/forums/showthread.php?t=275572</a>）<br />\n用簡轉繁字體（先將firmware update到最新<br />\n<a href=\"http://jdev.tw/blog/5389/kindle-customized-font\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjdev.tw%2Fblog%2F5389%2Fkindle-customized-font&d=JdofEqXGygwe9bBNhTug2ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=52eea411\" target=\"_blank\">http://jdev.tw/blog/5389/kindle-customized-font</a>）<br />\n<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">係kobo/Google買左書，點將佢放入Kindle睇？</span><br />\nCalibre幫到你<br />\n<a href=\"https://iamfugue.net/kindle-google-play/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiamfugue.net%2Fkindle-google-play%2F&d=JdofEqXGygwe9bBNhTug2ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4fa8c72e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://iamfugue.net/kindle-google-play/</a><br />\n<br />\n6.<span style=\"color: red;\">想橫排轉直排？</span><br />\n可以用呢個網轉<br />\n<a href=\"http://ebook.cdict.info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Febook.cdict.info&d=JdofEqXGygwe9bBNhTug2ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=64cd95f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ebook.cdict.info</a>（天火藏書）<br />\n或者用番Calibre嘅簡轉繁plugin都有呢個功能<br />\n<br />\n詳細教學（感謝海綿寶寶巴打）<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>我隨便分享下我做法（唔知有冇更好嘅做法）<br />\n我用mac版calibre，應該同windows一樣<br />\n<br />\n1. calibre&gt;偏好設定&gt;取得外掛&gt;搜尋格：traditional&lt;-&gt;Simplified Chinese Converter&gt;安裝之後重開軟件<br />\n<br />\n2. 然後拉你本簡體書入calibre (唔講deDRM，要解書另文講好啲）<br />\n乜格式都好，轉一次檔做azw3先 （個別轉換，輸出格式揀azw3）<br />\n（之後我會刪剩azw3，統一用azw3，因為上網啲人話mobi唔支援直排?）<br />\n<br />\n3. 右制&gt;編輯書藉&gt;plugins&gt;convert chinese text...<br />\n自己按需求揀設定，繁體，直排<br />\n<br />\n4. 轉完之後應該就可以，但我自己遇到多一個問題，應該係個plugin寫唔好(可能mac先有依個問題)，佢啲標點喺kindle度睇會九十度轉咗......<br />\n所以我會喺 偏好設定&gt;轉檔設定&gt;搜尋與取代，改左啲標點<br />\n例如：<br />\n︐ 轉做，<br />\n︓ 轉做：<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;轉做⋯⋯<br />\n︒轉做。<br />\n<br />\n另加： 如果想邊界攞盡啲，我會喺 外觀&gt;樣式 加以下一段：<br />\n@page {<br />\nmargin: 2%;<br />\n}<br />\n不過喺kindle就變相冇得改margin<br />\n上網有人討論更多CSS，不過唔講咁多，未必有用<br />\n之後再轉一次檔就完成<br />\n<br />\n5. 另外我會裝思源黑體睇（上網搵個字型，拉入font folder，要更新firmware做最新先有），咁樣啲標點先會置中而唔係側埋一邊<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到新手嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n7.<span style=\"color: red;\">廣告版（with Special offer)同非廣告版( without Special offer)有咩分別?</span><br />\n<br />\n廣告版同非廣告版嘅機能係完全一樣<br />\n分別只係在於一個待機時會有廣告畫面<br />\n所以廣告版會平幾舊<br />\n而廣告只會係待機畫面同揀書meun先會出現<br />\n你唔洗擔心會唔會睇睇下書迫人睇廣告<br />\n<br />\n但如果有書套嘅話<br />\n非廣告版一開書套就會自動著mon同解鎖<br />\n而廣告版只會自動著mon但需要手動解鎖<br />\n<br />\n買咗廣告版但唔想見廣告嘅話<br />\n都可以用Amazon客服講番<br />\n你係香港用唔著個special offer<br />\n佢就會幫你remove咗佢<br />\n<br />\n更新番我就已經買咗ppw 3開心使用中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e26ed00dc607a70dabcd7ece7cb4ab889a04c6f","tid":925884,"uid":43171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60aea498e92da0c1e6d2fc6e7125f9773183c5d4","tid":925884,"uid":36540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"開咗係吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難揾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36bf64a432af77c12853a617a8ff1bd10b6ef7c9","tid":925884,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60aea498e92da0c1e6d2fc6e7125f9773183c5d4","tid":925884,"uid":36540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"開咗係吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難揾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"屌sor<img src=\"/as