rc=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:26:13.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389f758749c6227b487227e6096d0bccfa02a9f5","tid":925884,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:27:55.000Z","msg":"[選擇困難症]買唔買Kindle好(3)暨交流區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bPPRKS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bPPRKS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fcf35d89c37ba98cc426d1986377cd5835e9a8de","tid":925884,"uid":58618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:52:04.000Z","msg":"想問readmoo d書係咪唔可以拎出黎放入calibre?<br />\n因為我買左部likebook mars 諗住可以係唔同平台買書方便d,但唔識拉佢出黎<br />\n<br />\n另外想問下amazon cn 係咪一定要大陸電話number先開到?"},{"pid":"629a75f98bdf02f1ce53c20946afbb6a40b01761","tid":925884,"uid":128451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:46:19.000Z","msg":"blackfriday部日版已經收到幾日<br />\n廣告版，預咗會有日本廣告，但係開咗日亞account都無廣告<br />\n之後開個中亞account反而有中國廣告<br />\n聽講日版廣告好靚想見識下<br />\n可以點做"},{"pid":"29e7ce0abf952ff157f73bf9b644b70cde4860d2","tid":925884,"uid":142247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"629a75f98bdf02f1ce53c20946afbb6a40b01761","tid":925884,"uid":128451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:46:19.000Z","msg":"blackfriday部日版已經收到幾日<br />\n廣告版，預咗會有日本廣告，但係開咗日亞account都無廣告<br />\n之後開個中亞account反而有中國廣告<br />\n聽講日版廣告好靚想見識下<br />\n可以點做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:52:49.000Z","msg":"To subscribe to Special Offers:<br />\n<br />\nGo to Manage Your Content and Devices.<br />\nSelect Your Devices, and then click the device Actions button to the left of the device name.<br />\nNext to Special Offers, click Edit, and then click Subscribe.<br />\nThe next time you connect your Kindle device wirelessly, it will complete the process of subscribing your device to Special Offers.<br />\n<br />\nIf you purchased a device that did not have Special Offers and subscribe to them, you can later unsubscribe at any time at no charge.<br />\n<br />\n呢個係美亞嘅做法<br />\n我諗日亞應該都一樣<br />\n只係要對番啲譯名<br />\nbtw新post重開咗係呢度<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bPPRKS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bPPRKS</a>"},{"pid":"88199a5c004769754a2b1b97e639ddf011ac65e5","tid":925884,"uid":87576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:53:00.000Z","msg":"有無邊到可以有部實體機望下?"},{"pid":"aaea0d92198b265f3c5ac5feee091b0f1b54de25","tid":925884,"uid":157113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"629a75f98bdf02f1ce53c20946afbb6a40b01761","tid":925884,"uid":128451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:46:19.000Z","msg":"blackfriday部日版已經收到幾日<br />\n廣告版，預咗會有日本廣告，但係開咗日亞account都無廣告<br />\n之後開個中亞account反而有中國廣告<br />\n聽講日版廣告好靚想見識下<br />\n可以點做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"我都係日版<br />\n你點整到無廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日版CS唔肯幫你remove special offer"},{"pid":"e59aa522d21e493ad354fbdcfe45dba7e40d2048","tid":925884,"uid":82157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"想問下最新呢個paperwhite 藍芽功能支唔支援有mic嘅耳機？懷疑緊係咪部新機有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed560b1cae268ee51acd3c5682bf95758e8518a7","tid":925884,"uid":164050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:19:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}